text: Olivia Kate Cooke (born 27 December 1993) is an English actress. She is known for her starring role as Emma Decody in the A&E; drama thriller series Bates Motel and as Becky Sharp in the period drama miniseries Vanity Fair. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1993 births Category:Actors from London Category:British child actors Category:British movie actors Category:British television actors Category:Living people Category:People from Oldham
